				    "======================================$N"
				    "$N"

				    "This is based on the following analysis:$N"
				    "$N"
				    "  If So = 64 and NewSize is 75 and OldSize is 50.$N"
				    "  Then Sn = So * ( NewSize / OldSize )$N"
				    "  If So = 32 and OldSize = 50, then 100% size is S100 = 32 * 2 = 64$N"
				    "  Then S100 * .75 = 48, so Sn = 32 * ( 1 / (1 / 2) )  * (3/4) = 32 * 2 * (3/4) = 32 * 3 / 2 = 16 * 3 = 48$N"

				    "";
				N: MOV(LINE.RECIPE.BATCH.SIZE_REM,OLD_BATCH_SIZE)[MOV(1,SIZE_FACTOR) ,GRT(OLD_BATCH_SIZE,0) DIV(NEW_BATCH_SIZE,OLD_BATCH_SIZE,SIZE_FACTOR) ];
